      <h3>Senior Sessions</h3>
      <p>All senior collections include a private online gallery for sharing and download and print release.</p>
      <p><strong>Senior Mini Session — $350:</strong> 45 minutes. 1 location. 15 digital images — fast, fun, and affordable.</p>
      <p><strong>Senior Full Session — $600:</strong> The ultimate senior experience — 2 hours. 1 location. 25+ digital images. $20 product credit.</p>
      <p><strong>Senior Split Session — $700:</strong> Same full session split across two dates — perfect for seasonal variety. 2 sessions. 2 dates. 50+ digital images. $30 product credit.</p>
      <p><strong>Senior DUO Session — $700:</strong> Two seniors, one epic session. Individual and duo shots included. 2 hours. 1 location. 25+ digital images each. $20 product credit each.</p>

      <h3>Family Sessions</h3>
      <p>All family collections include a private online gallery for sharing and download and print release.</p>
      <p><strong>Family Mini Session — $175:</strong> Perfect for holiday cards or just because. 30 minutes. 1 location. 10 digital images.</p>
      <p><strong>Family Full Session — $300:</strong> Bring the family and let's have some fun! 1 hour. 1 location. 25+ digital images. $20 product credit.</p>
      <p><strong>Milestone Sessions — $300:</strong> Maternity, engagements, birthdays. 1 hour. 1 location. 25+ digital images. $20 product credit.</p>

      <h3>Weddings</h3>
      <p><strong>Silver — $1,200:</strong> 6 hours of coverage on your wedding day.</p>
      <p><strong>Gold — $2,500:</strong> Engagement session. 8 hours of coverage. $50 product credit.</p>
      <p><strong>Platinum — $3,500:</strong> Engagement session. Full day coverage. Second photographer. $100 product credit.</p>
      <p><strong>The Signing — $150:</strong> Micro wedding. 20 minutes. The ceremony, the signing, the first kiss. 15+ digital images.</p>
      <p><strong>The Moment — $300:</strong> Micro wedding. Ceremony plus portraits and group photos. 30+ digital images.</p>
    </section>

